 &HT;    50 YEARS OF CHINA BY THE NUMBERS
 &HT;    With CHINA-MAO-0929.
 &HT;    Moving in both (i) International and (l) Lifestyle categories.
 &HT;    By MARCIA KUNSTEL and JOSEPH ALBRIGHT 
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service 
<TEXT>
<P>
   BEIJING _ The following are some statistics that show how China
has changed since the founding of the People's Republic of China 50
years ago.
</P>
