   CHIEF. Live feature on either Gunther Cunningham news
conference, Cris Dishman or Rashaan Sheehee working with needy kids
in Independence. Randy Covitz. 18-20.
</P>
<P>
   POZ. Joe Posnanski column on why the Royals' Carlos Beltran
should be the AL Rookie of the Year.
</P>
<P>
   ROYALS. Cleveland at Kansas City, 7:05 p.m. Howard Richman.
16-18.
</P>
<P>
   NLPEN. Finally, baseball has a pennant race again. Houston and
Cincinnati, tied with 94-63 records, square off in a two-game
series that will go a long way in determining the NL Central
champion and baseball's last playoff participant. Steven Rock.
18-20.
</P>
