<P>
   Finding accommodations during the millennium celebration can be
difficult. One solution is to seek out villas, condos, or private
homes. On St. Barthelemy, the small Caribbean isle, rates at hotels
for the celebration have been doubled in many cases. However, St.
Barth Properties (800-421-3396) reports there are properties where
