great shape, in fact in the top 1 percent of his age group and in
the top 5 percent for a 40-year-old man, his doctor says in a
medical report. And the doctor says there is no physical evidence
that the Texas governor and Republican presidential hopeful ever
regularly used drugs. By CLAY ROBISON.
