12,000-foot runway,'' he said, pointing to the barren land that is
bordered by a dirty drainage ditch. Welch is the executive director
of the Brazoria County Partnership, and he's hoping to catch the
big one: a huge spaceport that can send satellites and other cargo
into outer space. By L.M. SIXEL.
