<SLUG> BC-MILLENNIUM0929-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    PLANS ANNOUNCED FOR MILLENNIUM CELEBRATION IN NATION'S CAPITAL
 &HT;    With Photo
 &HT;    By BOB DART
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ Promising ``no ordinary party'' for ``no ordinary
time,'' First Lady Hillary Rodham Clinton on Tuesday invited
America to a Y2K bash in the nation's capital.
</P>
