<P>
   The Fort Worth Star-Telegram plans to move the following stories
for clients of the NYTimes News Service for AMs of Wednesday, Sept.
29, and thereafter. If you have any questions, please call Lou
Hudson, Tom Uhler, Paul Wagner or Jim Peipert on the
