   UNDATED _ Questions about the comic strip ``Pogo,'' how to
obtain a recording of the Bob and Ray comedy routine ``Slow Talkers
of America'' and how to contact Henry Cisneros. By ROGERS
CADENHEAD. Story has moved in ``l'' lifestyle category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   KID CRAFTS-FALL &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Yes, we know. Halloween is still a month away, but
it's not too early to get into the autumn spirit with some family
craft activities for the weekends ahead. Here are three of our
favorites: one for the very young, one appropriate for more steady
hands, and one even older kids will find cool. Start now and enjoy
them through October. By ALYSON WARD. Story will move in ``l''
lifestyle category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
