<HEADLINE>
ARIANNA'S READY TO GIVE OF HERSELF
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Eds: This story also moved in the ``l'' lifestyle file)  
 By LEAH GARCHIK  
 c.1999 San Francisco Chronicle
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; Arianna Huffington &LR;  threw a luncheon recently at her Brentwood
residence for Sen.  &UR; John McCain &LR;  and his new book, ``Faith of My
Fathers,'' and to introduce the author to her best and brightest
pals.
