<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-28 21:39 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9467 &Cx1f; tib-z
u k BC-DOWD-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      09-28 0723
