<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-28 21:42 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9469 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i BC-RUSSIA-REFUGEES-ART-7     09-28 1139
